Task 2: Test whether the first page of the website loads correctly and whether basic navigation works based on the example data provided in the Task.
Task 3: Test the elements and integrity of ALL pages. This includes verifying the presence and correctness of all specified elements on each page as per the requirements:

- Dashboard Page (ID: dashboard-page): featured-jobs (Div), browse-jobs-button (Button), my-applications-button (Button), companies-button (Button)
- Job Listings Page (ID: listings-page): search-input (Input), category-filter (Dropdown), location-filter (Dropdown), jobs-grid (Div), view-job-button-{job_id} (Button for each job)
- Job Details Page (ID: job-details-page): job-title (H1), company-name (Div), job-description (Div), salary-range (Div), apply-now-button (Button)
- Application Form Page (ID: application-form-page): applicant-name (Input), applicant-email (Input), resume-upload (File Input), cover-letter (Textarea), submit-application-button (Button)
- Application Tracking Page (ID: tracking-page): applications-table (Table), status-filter (Dropdown), view-application-button-{app_id} (Button for each application), back-to-dashboard (Button)
- Companies Directory Page (ID: companies-page): companies-list (Div), search-company-input (Input), view-company-button-{company_id} (Button for each company), back-to-dashboard (Button)
- Company Profile Page (ID: company-profile-page): company-info (Div), company-jobs (Div), jobs-list (Div), view-job-button-{job_id} (Button), back-to-companies (Button)
- Resume Management Page (ID: resume-page): resumes-list (Div), upload-resume-button (Button), resume-file-input (File Input, hidden), delete-resume-button-{resume_id} (Button for each resume), back-to-dashboard (Button)
- Search Results Page (ID: search-results-page): search-query-display (Div), results-tabs (Div), job-results (Div), company-results (Div), no-results-message (Div)
